<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[٢٩٨٥ ـ أبو كبشة بن [ .... ]</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span>]<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
